article_title: Photos: Rochester vs. Chicago Phillips Class 4A football title game

og.description: Rochester defeated Chicago Phillips 49-28 to take their fifth straight Class 4A state football championship on Friday, Nov. 28, 2014, at Memorial Stadium in Champaign.
